product packages for corporate pension schemes which include corporate pension plan design management of pension policyholders and recipients and asset management and custody as well as investment solutions and review of pension schemes introduction and management of defined contribution pension schemes and disposit mizuho trust  banking co ltd engages in custody and administration pension trust and asset management businesses in japan the company offers custody and administration services related to asset management for money trusts pecuniary trusts investment trusts securities trusts and other types of trusts as well as master trust services it also provides services and product packages for corporate pension schemes which include corporate pension plan design management of pension policyholders and recipients and asset management and custody as well as investment solutions and review of pension schemes introduction and management of defined contribution pension schemes and dispositiontype employee stock ownership plans retirement benefits and compensation plans for senior executives in addition the company offers asset management products using various investment targets and methods including hedge funds privately laced real estate investment funds concentrated investment funds and package products and equity and fixed income products alternatives and packaged funds it operates through a network of  branches and  subbranches the company was founded in  and is headquartered in tokyo japan mizuho trust  banking co ltd is a subsidiary of mizuho financial group inc detailed description  yaesuchuokutokyo  japanfounded in  employees phone     wwwmizuhotbcojp key executives for mizuho trust  banking co ltd mr tetsuo iimori chief executive officer president and director age  mr isao nakamura managing exec officer  jt head of strategic planning financial control  accounting group age  mr makoto okayama deputy president and executive officer mr nobumitsu watanabe managing 