harge of trust  banking managing executive officer sumito yasuhara’s position has been changed from general manager of trust business department v to the new position of general manager of trust business department v executive officer atsunori tsurumaki’s position has been changed from general manager of trust business department vii to the new position of general manager of nagoya branch executive officer shinichi iwamura’s position has been changed from general manager of investment  portfolio management coordination department to the new position of general manager of investment  portfolio management coordination department executive officer kazuma ohe’s position has been changed from general manager of real estate business coordination department to the new position of general manager of real estate business department iv executive officer tomoyasu kikuno’s position has been changed from general manager of branch administration department to the new position of general manager of fukuoka branch executive officer shinya matake’s position has been changed from general manager of corporate planning department to the new position of general manager of corporate planning department executive officer and kazuyuki akiyama’s position has been changed from general manager of consulting department to the new position of general manager of trust business department vii executive officer the company announced the retirement of makio muramoto as in charge of trust  banking managing executive officer takashi kamada as head of retail  business banking division managing executive officer eijiro yamanaka as general manager of fukuoka branch executive officer masanori takahata as general manager of real estate business department ii executive officer takashi otsuka as general manager of trust business department iii executive officer these all changes are effective from april   the company also announced the retirement of tsuyoshi hatsuzawa as member of the board of directors eff